## Singularity image - builds from Docker image, so build that first.
Bootstrap: docker
From: ronwalf/htntranslate:hpddl

%post
## All done in the Docker image

%runscript
    htnunlift $@

%labels
    Name   htnunlift-hpddl: Part of the HTN to PDDL translator for HPDDL (a pre-HDDL hierarchical task network description language). Takes a domain and problem file, and produces a domain/problem pair where the initial task network is a single ground task (a requirement of the translator).
    Author ronwalf@volus.net
    Version 0.1
